*             Mean density     [kg/m3] 5520.0000 *
*          Surface gravity      [m/s2]    9.8066 *
*              Bond albedo                0.3850 *
*         Solar irradiance      [W/m2] 1367.0000 *
*   Black-body temperature         [K]  247.3000 *
